title: Shoot to High it May Collapse

description:
Monday 4/3- Back to the work the week and back to another segment of "Shoot your Shot." This time a listener name Tone is trying to shoot his shot at his ex's sister, but, things did not go as he planned. Also, after Charlamagne gave Donkey of the Day to a crack head, Basil Eleby, because he was connected to the collapse of the Atlanta Bridge we opened the phones to see who is our listeners favorite crack heads of all time.
